{
  "stem": "2533.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were waiting for the water to-- to heat up for the washing because everything had to be manual done, the washing, and boiled, and all that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I didn't see the other girls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were four girls in the laundry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't see the German coming in the laundry, and I wasn't fast enough.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I couldn't work even then because the water wasn't hot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But my ear was aching so badly, so I was standing near that-- that where the copper was, where the water was heating.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he took me out from that-- from the laundry to that [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Wagner. ?] And [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Wagner ?] was on the place where they had all the wood for the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was called the holzplatz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Wagner ?] was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said to him, but in German, what shall we do with that little one?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He told me to bend down and to lift up even my skirt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was such a tall fellow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there, what do you call, the-- the whips, they were steel inside with leather on top.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the whip was so long, nearly-- you know, when he's starting to hit me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I would have been taller, maybe I would have got it more on my backside.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But being so short, I got it most in the waist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So every time the whip came around to the front, later on I had blisters.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I didn't know that-- then that something happened, you know, to my kidney.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I got back to work, the girls helped me to put cold compresses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was so sore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't sit.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I couldn't lie.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But somehow I managed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we had a dentist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I was complaining about the ear.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
